# 🟢 Problem 2: Food Delivery

```java
abstract class Restaurant {
    abstract void placeOrder();
    abstract void prepareFood();
    abstract void deliveryTime();
}

class FastFood extends Restaurant {
    void placeOrder() {
        System.out.println("Fast food ordered");
    }
    void prepareFood() {
        System.out.println("Prepared quickly");
    }
    void deliveryTime() {
        System.out.println("20 minutes");
    }
}

class TraditionalFood extends Restaurant {
    void placeOrder() {
        System.out.println("Traditional food ordered");
    }
    void prepareFood() {
        System.out.println("Fresh cooking");
    }
    void deliveryTime() {
        System.out.println("45 minutes");
    }
}
```

