# 🟢 Problem 4: Ride Service

```java
abstract class Ride {
    double baseFare = 50;
    abstract void fare(double d);
}

class Bike extends Ride {
    void fare(double d) {
        System.out.println("Bike Fare: " + (baseFare + d * 10));
    }
}

class Car extends Ride {
    void fare(double d) {
        System.out.println("Car Fare: " + (baseFare + d * 20));
    }
}
```

